Rate this house with an emoji 😊 is a unique concept located in Switzerland. The design is inspired by the natural slopes and lush forest of the surrounding landscape. Skylights play a prominent theme in the house - particularly in the bedroom, living room, and home theater.

Which room in this incredible architectural masterpiece is your absolute favorite? You can only pick one! 😉

📷 @miladeshtiyaghi
